Name: contact support

description: the user will be able to send inquirys to the admin.

players: user

preconditions: the user have to be already registered and login.

Basic flow:
	1) login
	2) scroll down the screen
	3) press "contact us"
	4) fill your name and your email in the designated boxes.
  	5) fill your messege in the place desined for it.
  	6) press send.

alternate flow:
------
exception flow:
If information was put incorrectly or empty inputs, red notice and message will pop up

post conditions:
the messege will be sent to the admin.
